Follow `AGENTS.md`.

- Keep the project scoped to `npm run dump:empreendimento-data`, `npm run format:empreendimento-data`, and `npm run full:empreendimento-data`.
- Do not reintroduce removed Fastify API, Playwright capture, or standalone empreendimento-list dump tooling unless explicitly requested.
- Preserve generated JSON data unless regeneration is part of the task.
- Never commit real `.env` secrets.
